Description: Create a directory, populate it with data, build models, forecast rodent populations, and visualize the results. This package provides the functionality underlying the Portal Predictions Project <https://github.com/weecology/portalpredictions> and website <https://portal.naturecast.org> as well as support for exploring and developing new models in sandbox environments.
URL: https://weecology.github.io/portalcasting/, https://github.com/weecology/portalcasting
